title: Trenden Nation Army by The Zeit Stripes 7/29: ScarJo, Shake Shack, Jared Leto, Chicken Wings, Sunisa Lee, Fred Durst
itunes:title: Trenden Nation Army by The Zeit Stripes 7/29: ScarJo, Shake Shack, Jared Leto, Chicken Wings, Sunisa Lee, Fred Durst
description:
In this edition of Trenden Nation Army by The Zeit Stripes, Miles and Super Producer Anna Hossnieh discuss ScarJo suing Disney for messing with her money, Shake Shack requiring vaccines for employees AND customers, Jared Leto being unrecognizable in new movie 'House of Gucci', National Chicken Wing Day, Sunisa Lee winning all-around gold, and Fred Durst's new look.
